    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The exterior has noticeable rust, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and some of the dashboard electronics are non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent oil leak and the transmission shifts roughly. This car is ideal for someone looking for a dedicated project or for valuable spare parts.",
