    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the factory limited-slip differential translates torque into precise corner exits. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, this driver-focused example offers exceptional turn-in response and high-RPM mechanical harmony. Recent valve clearance adjustments and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul ensure peak thermal efficiency and valvetrain longevity for the next enthusiast owner.",
