    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior paint still holds a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard use. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the upholstery is clean and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the responsive touchscreen interface, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, backed by a complete service history and a recently completed multi-point inspection. It has been garage-kept and treated with care, making it an excellent choice for someone seeking a dependable, high-quality ride without the new-car price tag.",
